" Alternate way to save 
nnoremap <silent> <S-x> :w<CR>

"--------------------------------------------------------------

" " Alternate way to quit
nnoremap <silent> <C-Q> :wq!<CR>

"---------------------------------------------------------------

"  Use control-c instead of escape
nnoremap <silent> <C-c> <Esc>

"---------------------------------------------------------------

"Use Shift z --> w!
nnoremap <silent> <S-z> :w!<CR>

"---------------------------------------------------------------

"Use Control n- for quit
nnoremap <silent> <C-n> :q<CR>

"---------------------------------------------------------------

"Use Control m- For quit!
nnoremap <silent> <C-m> :q!<CR>

"---------------------------------------------------------------
"Run Terminal In Nvim With Control t-
nnoremap <silent> <C-t> :term<CR>


"--------------------------------------------------------------"

" Run NNN With Control y-
nnoremap <silent> <C-y> :Np<CR>
"---------------------------------------------------------------"
"Run NerdTree With Shift + C"
nnoremap <silent> <S-c> :NERDTree




















